      "id": "PopularPost102409",
      "post_content": "Well, it's sorta no FTK, but the kavu was always....really really good. This is like a mediocre version. Half the effect (at a different time), half the power, half the toughess....and only 1 less cost? Plus the effect works at the wrong time. It would be much better if it was when it came into play, so you could kill your opponent's BOP/cobra/heirarch/whatever early.",
