      "id": "PopularPost325620",
      "post_content": "I used to run this in my burn deck, but it never really saw too much use. Letting your opponent choose when (or if) they wanted to take burn is a pain in the ass. The Firefiend is never going to die when there's a creature you'd like to nuke, and it's never going to do damage while there's a creature with more than 2 toughness out there.",
